honest with me, Dave.

66
00:06:45,854 --> 00:06:49,130
Have you changed any
since you were 14?

67
00:06:49,334 --> 00:06:52,884
Hey, I'm all for you
getting laid, believe me.

68
00:07:04,817 --> 00:07:06,409
Morning.

69
