You gotta try these. They're hydroponic.
Grown in water.

70
00:07:10,498 --> 00:07:13,410
I know the guy who grows them.
He's a big supplier to the co-op.

71
00:07:13,618 --> 00:07:16,770
- So my peaches are no good?
- What?

72
00:07:16,979 --> 00:07:19,413
No, they're fine.

73
00:07:26,220 --> 00:07:29,418
